deno.json
  warning [deprecated-node-modules-dir-boolean] deno.json uses the boolean form `"nodeModulesDir": true`, which is deprecated since Deno 2.0. Deno currently interprets it as "auto".
    fix: replace `"nodeModulesDir": true` with `"nodeModulesDir": "auto"` (the mode Deno currently derives from the boolean)

